content: I think I'll try to do the 4-7-8 breathing exercise right before bed to help me relax and prepare for sleep. I'll set a reminder on my phone to remind me to do it every night. For Headspace, I'll try to do the meditation sessions in the morning, right after I wake up, to help me start my day on a positive note. I'll also try to commit to doing it 3-4 times a week to start, and then see how it goes.
